title: K.Lee's Wife Almost Died And He Blames Her
description:
You guys, Khristian has done it again. Pack your bags K.Lee because you’re back in the dog house. Or at least that’s what happens when you let your wife choke. 
He was editing audio at home and his wife was in the kitchen cooking, when all of a sudden, she started coughing and he didn't save her.
